        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/panama-canal-ricaurte-vasquez-pete-hegseth-miraflores-locks-visit.png" alt="Panama Canal administrator Ricaurte Vásquez next to Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth during a visit to the Miraflores locks of the Panama Canal in Panama City" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
